<p><strong>Title :</strong> Humanisme et Esthétique/Humanism and Aesthetics<br />
<strong>Author :</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drtesla" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2194347); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2194347&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721478" alt="DrTesla" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2194347)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drtesla" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2194347); return false;">DrTesla</a></span><br />
